Vel BP &gt; Fungi and 175BW after 50% health<br>
Fungi alone &gt; Vel BP during combat, running (including running away to a zoneline with something is beating on you) or other times when you can't click.<br>
<br>
Fungi and Vel BP &gt; BW at any level with any AA if you run out of bandages or can't carry any. <p><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=257207" *****"text-decoration: none">Khuzdul</A><br>
